high_descs: Turn around. When you reach the end of the sink, cross to the right and then to the left.
Approach the sink. Take the onion from the sink.
Go back to the onion. Turn around to face the fridge.
Open the refrigerator. Place the onion on the first level, near the bottom. Close the bottom. Wait ten seconds. Open the door. Take out the onion. Close the door.
Place the onion on the left side of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Find an onion, cool it. Place it back in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around to walk to the counter next to the sink.
Pick up the red onion from the counter.
Turn around to reach the fridge on the right.
Cool the onion in the fridge and take it out.
Turn right to reach the counter next to the sink.
Put the onion on the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the cooled onion on the sink.
